thread.title: Government Bond Prices Edge Higher

author: Gunjan Banerji
title: Government Bond Prices Edge Higher
text:
U.S. government bond prices rose Monday, sending the yield on the benchmark 10-year U.S. Treasury note lower for a third straight session.
The 10-year yield slipped to 2.936% from 2.959% on Friday. Yields fall as bond prices rise.
